        </p>
        <p>
            This system not only improves responsiveness but also enables <strong>rigorous process tracking without manual workload overload.</strong> By integrating notifications with other management modules (sales, purchases, payments, inventory...), Movelys helps enhance transparency, trust, and productivity.
        </p>
        <p>
            Thus, notification management becomes a strategic lever for customer retention, internal organization, and continuous performance improvement.
        </p>
